  <h1>Understanding Anchor Tags in HTML</h1>

  <!-- Blog Introduction -->
  <p>
    In this demo blog, we will explore how to use the 
    <strong>anchor tag (&lt;a&gt;)</strong> in HTML to create links within a 
    webpage or to external resources.
  </p>

